data.description: Rarely available stunning Townhome in Manassas Park Station.  Home Features  3 Bed, 3 Full Bath,  1 Half bath, 2 Car Garage, Large Living Area, Gourmet kitchen , fully finished basement and nice backyard. Excellent location just Minutes to VRE, Shopping, Restaurants, 28, and I-66. Upon Entering the home, step up to Huge Gourmet Kitchen, Wood Floors, 5 Burner Cooktop, Wall Oven With Microwave . Large Living/Dining Room Combination With Hardwood Flooring. Relaxing Primary Bedroom With Tray Ceiling, and Walk-in Closet. Primary Bath Has Separate Soaking Tub and Shower. 2 Additional Nice Sized Bedrooms, Full Bath, and Bedroom Level Laundry With Front Loading Washer and Dryer completes The Upper Level. Lower Level Has a Recreation Room With fireplace wood flooring and Full Bath. Walk-Out To Back Yard. Community boasts a lot of amenities such pool, tot lot and waking trails.
